                <p className="text-base text-[#444] leading-[1.75] mb-4 last:mb-0">Mdcatemy may collaborate with Grammlogic or other academic partners for selected subjects such as English and Logical Reasoning. Where applicable, students may access lectures, quizzes, practice material, explanations, or related academic services through Grammlogic or partner platforms. Such platforms may collect or process user information according to their own privacy policies and terms.</p>
