                    <li className="flex items-start gap-3 py-2 border-b border-[#f5f5f5] last:border-b-0"><span className="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#F6C90E] shrink-0 mt-2.5"></span><span className="text-base text-[#444] leading-[1.65]">Cheating in tests</span></li>
